{"tid":834783,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[電視撚求救]要買天線但唔知買邊款","createTime":"2018-09-24T11:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T13:12:50.000Z","uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4520e7f91fe129c13cca1b44c635a9599b9630e9","tid":834783,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"有個ei8ht電視天線錦舊野，<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/192711_9226e018dd8fd62e7fdf43b0f6a05104.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F192711_9226e018dd8fd62e7fdf43b0f6a05104.png&h=1389b8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nout個到分左右，左邊條線就出到個天線位係廳睇到電視啦，如圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/192741_5383d46b405f4b6c20a70dfed12924c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F192741_5383d46b405f4b6c20a70dfed12924c8.png&h=27f8c6f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係右邊個條就唔係天線，如圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/192802_07384b8b9135468ae03c8582068487e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F192802_07384b8b9135468ae03c8582068487e7.png&h=d08a4484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試過插唔到入個電視天線個位，因為想買多個電視，想問下要買d咩產品令到out右出到個天線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5853becb0da8e901bd12f34313e8f9d7fdbc7f3","tid":834783,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"仲不個out2條線太短唔夠長，要延長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3e4e78ca2d10ae706473edbc2fdf5c8d847517","tid":834783,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5853becb0da8e901bd12f34313e8f9d7fdbc7f3","tid":834783,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"仲不個out2條線太短唔夠長，要延長<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm